data.description: Back on Market!   A spacious and wonderful home nestled in a charming north Avondale neighborhood.   Perfect location near the 101 and I-10 freeways, restaurants, shopping, sporting and entertainment venues.  You will love the curb appeal, the foyer and vaulted ceilings that welcome you as you walk in.  Home has fresh exterior and interior paint, new water heater and newer ac units.  Travertine flooring  throughout first level and laminate wood flooring upstairs.   3 bedrooms including primary upstairs in addition to a loft area, great for an office or kids play area.   Backyard offers an extended covered patio, a private pool, a pergola, RV gate and built in BBQ area.  Best priced home in the area.  Make an appt to see it today!
